# saug (Spatial Augmentation)
Spatial distortions for image augmentations

## Cite this library: 

@article{oskouei2024segmentation,
  title={Segmentation of Non-Small Cell Lung Carcinomas: Introducing DRU-Net and Multi-Lens Distortion},
